00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 62 =

20
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:45,420
Yuanheng.

21
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,780
Last time you said we would never meet again,

22
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:49,380
I thought…

23
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,540
I’m here for Princess.

24
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:51,980
Princess?

25
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:54,180
Take your time.

26
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,140
There are numerous interesting places

27
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:56,500
in such a bustling capital.

28
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:58,700
And today is the last day

29
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,340
of Lantern Festival.

30
00:01:59,340 --> 00:02:00,300
We have the most gorgeous lanterns

31
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:02,220
and the most boisterous carnival.

32
00:02:02,620 --> 00:02:03,340
Come on.

33
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:04,420
I’ll take you to the top floor

34
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:06,420
so you can see the whole venue.

35
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:07,180
This way.

36
00:02:12,189 --> 00:02:14,580
= Sumo =
Bravo! Take her down. Bravo!

37
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,740
Come on. Take her down.

38
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,391
Good.

39
00:02:38,875 --> 00:02:39,831
Yes, again.

40
00:02:41,258 --> 00:02:42,214
Bravo!

41
00:02:43,848 --> 00:02:45,376
Bravo!

42
00:02:55,768 --> 00:02:57,288
Bravo!

43
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,620
Okay. Thank you.

44
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:01,540
Thank you.

45
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:05,740
Thank you for being here.

46
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,700
For me?

47
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,420
Thank you, thank you.

48
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:54,340
Huaiji, you are here.

49
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:02,180
You go back first.

50
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,180
Go.

51
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,340
Let’s go back.

52
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:09,940
Otherwise

53
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:11,540
Mr. Liang might catch us.

54
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,260
I want

55
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:17,500
to try the food in Winehouse Fan.

56
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,100
There are food and wine prepared in the mansion.

57
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,300
I want to see more lanterns.

58
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,380
There are many lanterns in the mansion too.

59
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:36,980
But I want to sit in Winehouse Fan,

60
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:39,700
and eat food there

61
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,100
while watching the lanterns on the streets.

62
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:46,020
Sir,

63
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,580
your wife just wants you to stay longer with her

64
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,180
to hang around and have more fun.

65
00:04:50,340 --> 00:04:51,980
Why are you so dull?

66
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:53,540
You are lucky to marry such a beautiful girl,

67
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:55,260
yet you don’t even want to

68
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:57,180
spend more time with her?

69
00:04:58,660 --> 00:04:59,460
Exactly.

70
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:01,140
You said before

71
00:05:01,580 --> 00:05:02,940
you’ll be my shadow.

72
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:05,420
You’ll go wherever I go.

73
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:07,140
Now

74
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:10,300
you just say no to everything.

75
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,060
Does what you said before still count?

76
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,700
What a shy man.

77
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:24,180
Take him to Winehouse Fan

78
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:25,060
and have a seat there.

79
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:26,500
Let’s go.

80
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:33,980
Brother, if I leave with you now,

81
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:35,900
I don’t know

82
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:37,380
when I shall be able

83
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:39,100
to see the joys in common life.

84
00:06:20,780 --> 00:06:21,460
Please enjoy.

85
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,580
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
Is that a show?

86
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:31,660
All I saw

87
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,780
was half-naked women

88
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:34,740
fighting in public.

89
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,300
That is completely shameless.

90
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:39,180
That is called woman Sumo.

91
00:06:39,940 --> 00:06:41,740
It is part of the Lantern Show

92
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:43,260
every year.

93
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:46,025
His Majesty loves to watch that show

94
00:06:46,025 --> 00:06:46,791
when he goes to see lanterns at Xuande Gate.

95
00:06:47,296 --> 00:06:50,100
Even His Majesty

96
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,420
doesn’t think there is a problem.

97
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:54,700
The fact that His Majesty doesn’t think
there is a problem

98
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:56,700
is the biggest problem.

99
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,380
Among all the shows in the carnival,

100
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:06,220
woman Sumo is my favorite,

101
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,860
in which women can fight like men,

102
00:07:09,140 --> 00:07:09,980
instead of

103
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:11,140
playing instruments

104
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,300
or providing entertainments with dancing or singing

105
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,260
wearing heavy make-ups.

106
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:16,060
Wearing less in this kind of show

107
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:18,500
does not matter much.

108
00:07:21,420 --> 00:07:22,340
Besides,

109
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:23,820
there are many men

110
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:25,940
exposing their arms,

111
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:27,260
why can’t women

112
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,980
expose a little bit more of our skin?

113
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:31,900
= Sima Guang’s Wife =

114
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:43,020
Why bother to argue with a woman in public?

115
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:47,940
Let’s go.

116
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:52,980
I’ll write a proposal tonight

117
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,740
to report to His Majesty.

118
00:08:00,900 --> 00:08:02,100
This is Sima Guang.

119
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:04,500
I told you before.

120
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:07,340
When I was young, I sent a glazed cup to him for someone.

121
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:09,500
But when he opened it, it was broken.

122
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,420
Luckily he’s kind and tolerant

123
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,660
and didn’t blame me.

124
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,760
I heard that from you.

125
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,800
I thought

126
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,960
he must be an elegant and unconventional man.

127
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,720
But who knows

128
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,680
he’s such a

129
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,960
stagnant old man.

130
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:38,700
= Cao Yi’s Son Cao Ping =

131
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:54,820
Mrs. Yang,

132
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,580
Mrs. Yang, Princess hasn’t woken up yet.

133
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:57,580
Please wait for a moment outside.

134
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,300
Mrs. Yang.

135
00:08:58,580 --> 00:08:59,460
Move.

136
00:08:59,621 --> 00:09:00,543
Mrs. Yang.

137
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,180
Mrs. Yang.

138
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,580
Mr. Liang,

139
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:24,500
you are so attentive to Princess.

140
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,680
During daytime, you two are always inseparable.

141
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,600
At night,

142
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,280
you even come to her bedroom to serve her.

143
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:33,680
No wonder in the whole mansion,

144
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:34,960
only you are good enough

145
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,440
in Princess’s eyes.

146
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,080
Not everyone

147
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,720
has your capability and thinking.

148
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,840
Mr. Liang does not stay here every night.

149
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,560
Last night, Princess felt sick,

150
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,120
so I asked him to come here.

151
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,440
I was told

152
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,960
yesterday Princess and Mr. Liang

153
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,920
sneaked out secretly,

154
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,560
had fun for a whole day,

155
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,360
and came back at midnight.

156
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,920
So Mr. Liang was invited to come here

157
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,040
just because Princess felt sick?

158
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,920
Do you have extraordinary medical skills

159
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,320
and some secret therapy

160
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,120
that can’t be seen

161
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,160
by others,

162
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:14,040
so you sent all the maids and eunuchs

163
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,400
to wait in the yard

164
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,520
and no one is allowed to come in?

165
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,480
Who are you to me?

166
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,160
Do I need to report to you

167
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,680
for summoning a server,

168
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,160
get your approval

169
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,280
and be supervised by you?

170
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,120
Who am I to you?

171
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,000
I am your husband’s mother!

172
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,520
I am your mother-in-law!

173
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,200
I am just like your mother!

174
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,720
Well, well,

175
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:40,720
a newly-wedded woman invited some random guy

176
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,520
to her room to stay overnight,

177
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,000
can’t the mother-in-law

178
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,640
ask about it?

179
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,000
What a mother-in-law?

180
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,160
What a mad woman!

181
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,960
How dare you to compare yourself to my parents?

182
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,160
Someone,

183
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,560
tell her the rules!

184
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,360
Mrs. Yang,

185
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,640
after the marriage of Princess,

186
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,120
everyone in the Prince Consort’s family, except himself,
shall lower their family rankings by one level.

187
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,920
What a stupid rule!

188
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,320
Yes,

189
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,240
there are many rules in the imperial family.

190
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,600
But can rules override ethics?

191
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,760
Once married, the Emperor’s daughter

192
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,560
is someone’s wife.

193
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,920
I never see

194
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,400
any wife

195
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:20,280
can walk all over her mother-in-aw

196
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,280
and refuse to call her mother.

197
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:24,120
Go to ask your parents

198
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,120
if this is how they want you

199
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,480
to serve me!

200
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:28,880
What?

201
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,680
Mother-in-law is disciplining her daughter-in-law,

202
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,760
is that something wrong?

203
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,720
People at His Majesty’s court

204
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:35,920
are civilized men who talk big,

205
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,760
I’d like to ask them

206
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,920
to give some comments

207
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,080
on what happened today.

208
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,920
I’d like to ask

209
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,640
who broke the rules

210
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:45,720
and wronged the family ranking.

211
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:50,080
She broke into my bedroom

212
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:53,320
and slandered me verbally with extreme rudeness.

213
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,360
Kick her out!

214
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,560
What are you doing?

215
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,960
What are you doing? What are you doing?

216
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,960
Don’t you dare to touch me! Don’t you dare!

217
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,520
Don’t you dare! Don’t you dare!

218
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,440
You!

219
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,440
Let go of me!

220
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,680
Kick her out!

221
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,560
Princess.

222
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,120
Good news from the palace.

223
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,720
At 6:15 a.m. today,

224
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:17,200
Lady of Wenxi County gave birth to the Ninth Princess.

225
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,800
The handwritten order of Her Highness

226
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,400
asks Princess to go to the palace.

227
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,640
I lost again.

228
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,520
You are still not calm inside.

229
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,840
I’m impressed by Your Majesty.

230
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,480
On the day of the coup,

231
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,480
Your Majesty, you were calmer than me,

232
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:07,160
because you have a better vision than me,

233
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,640
and you can see things through.

234
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:11,040
You knew they didn’t have many people.

235
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,160
But today…

236
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,720
What should I worry about?

237
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,080
I can’t have a son

238
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:20,160
so I will grieve over it and
get severely sick again?

239
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,880
And even if this happens, don’t you worry.

240
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,560
I told you already

241
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,880
if I fall ill and can’t recover,

242
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,400
Zongshi shall succeed to the throne.

243
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,560
Actually

244
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,840
if today I did have a son,

245
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,160
it would bring me

246
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,520
more struggles and confusion.

247
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,960
How many years will it take for him to grow up?

248
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,200
If I can’t wait that long,

249
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,760
a young emperor will put the country
into instability.

250
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,880
You are only 50,

251
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:57,200
what nonsense are you talking about.

252
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,720
I am really happy today.

253
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,040
After so many years,

254
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:07,000
I finally have another daughter.

255
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,400
Now the Ninth Princess is born,

256
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,600
the ceremony prepared

257
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,520
for the birth of an imperial son

258
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,440
will be held as planned?

259
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,720
As planned.

260
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,760
Your Majesty, Princes is here.

261
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:30,040
Tell the wet nurse to take the Ninth Princess out

262
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,120
to show her sister.

263
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:33,240
She

264
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:35,000
looks just like Huirou

265
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,280
when she was born.

266
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,600
I’ll stitch the three big pearls

267
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,880
father gave me

268
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,840
on the flower heart

269
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:51,960
and embroider the edge with golden lines.

270
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:53,960
Silly girl.

271
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,320
This is a baby’s bellyband.

272
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:58,240
You can’t just sew

273
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,400
those hard things on it

274
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,720
just for a good-looking.

275
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,120
Can she

276
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,480
wear anklet with golden bells?

277
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,800
When will she grow hair?

278
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,080
I want to braid her hair.

279
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,640
Mother,

280
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,160
do you remember

281
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:18,200
when I started to speak?

282
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,560
Half year old?

283
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,240
One year old?

284
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:24,880
When can she call me

285
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:26,200
sister?

286
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,080
Huirou

287
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,080
really likes your little sister.

288
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,520
I’ll come back often to see her.

289
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,240
Does father spoil

290
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:38,000
her more

291
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:39,320
than the way he spoiled me?

292
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,960
Will he ask her not to eat too much candied fruits?

293
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,440
Then I’ll fawn on her with candied fruits

294
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,920
so that I can be her favorite one.

295
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:50,080
Look at you, so childish.

296
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,840
When you become a mother,

297
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,840
your children…

298
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:00,560
Huirou,

299
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:04,600
actually, when a woman has children,

300
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:07,240
you’ll devote most of your heart on your children.

301
00:16:08,160 --> 00:16:09,600
If you have two or three kids,

302
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,280
you’ll be too busy with teaching them all day long

303
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,360
to even think about your husband.

304
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:33,920
I’ll treat the children of my husband

305
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,480
the same way Your Highness

306
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,880
cared for me and taught me

307
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:38,040
in the future.

308
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:57,591
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =
I impeached Bao Zheng not because of my personal hatred.

309
00:16:57,974 --> 00:17:00,858
Every word I said is out of my devotion
to public interests.

310
00:17:01,183 --> 00:17:02,808
I mean it.

311
00:17:03,174 --> 00:17:05,473
I hope Your Majesty can understand.

312
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:18,940
His Majesty insists on not taking back

313
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:20,140
his appointment of Supervisor of Finance,

314
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,340
and Bao Zheng insists on rejecting it.

315
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:24,180
Today after the court,

316
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:26,700
His Majesty sent an officer to Bao Zheng Mansion

317
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:28,660
to summon him to the Side Hall to meet His Majesty.

318
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:31,740
Will His Majesty persuade Bao Zheng

319
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:33,220
or the other way around?

320
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,660
I believe

321
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:38,220
His Majesty will persuade Bao Zheng.

322
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:41,140
You are so sure?

323
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:45,060
= Bao Zheng, courtesy name Xiren =
I impeached my colleagues outright,

324
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,860
but I did so out of public interest.

325
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:50,780
Mr. Ouyang said I’m stern and upright

326
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,260
with little knowledge. I agree.

327
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:53,820
I am not as knowledgeable

328
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,220
and literate as him.

329
00:17:56,620 --> 00:17:57,780
But he said

330
00:17:58,220 --> 00:18:00,020
I am appointed as the Supervisor
of Finance by Your Majesty

331
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:00,980
after I impeached two officials at this position,

332
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:03,740
which seems like I attacked my colleagues
to gain this position.

333
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:05,980
Your Majesty,

334
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:10,060
please understand me.

335
00:18:12,140 --> 00:18:14,620
I can’t take such an ill fame.

336
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,860
You said

337
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:21,140
you impeached your colleagues harshly

338
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:23,260
out of public interest.

339
00:18:24,860 --> 00:18:25,740
I think

340
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:30,340
Ouyang Xiu is just like you.

341
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:32,820
You shouldn’t mind him.

342
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:35,140
I don’t mind him,

343
00:18:35,820 --> 00:18:36,860
but I think

344
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,180
what Mr. Ouyang said

345
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:42,180
the way I evicted them looks like I pushed
them to the edge

346
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:44,660
will be the truth

347
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:47,220
to all the officials

348
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:48,620
if I really take this position

349
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:52,220
after I impeached two Supervisors of Finance.

350
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:59,100
Wei Zheng recommended talented people even if they are close to him.

351
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,300
I think

352
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:03,420
even if you can’t recommend yourself,

353
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:05,780
you shouldn’t treat a good reputation

354
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:08,220
more important than contribution to the court.

355
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:10,980
Having been an official for years,

356
00:19:11,180 --> 00:19:13,340
you are honest, upright, and capable.

357
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:15,900
If you don’t take the position to avoid arousing suspicion,

358
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:17,900
that will not appear magnanimous.

359
00:19:19,987 --> 00:19:20,500
I…

360
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:42,200
I can pay for your drink.

361
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:44,000
But just now we agreed

362
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,480
the one who lost shall pay.

363
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,640
Now we don’t know the result yet,

364
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:50,880
are you taking the award in advance?

365
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,120
I will win for sure.

366
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:56,360
Yongshu condemned him

367
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:57,880
so harshly at the court,

368
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,440
but he didn’t say anything back.

369
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,720
The second day he wrote a proposal

370
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,320
asking His Majesty to retract his order.

371
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,640
He read books all day long and refused to attend the court

372
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,280
to prove his innocence.

373
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,760
If he does take the position,

374
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,520
then pushing his colleagues to the edge

375
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:12,160
for the position proves to be true.

376
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,320
I don’t think he will take the position.

377
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:16,240
You

378
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,360
need to buy me two drinks then.

379
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,800
Why can’t you understand?

380
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:26,040
His Majesty wants him

381
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,640
to take the position with ill fame

382
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,560
so that he can work for the court.

383
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:30,960
Please come in.

384
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:39,600
His Majesty is forcing him to do so?

385
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:45,000
Well,

386
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:48,840
we can force His Majesty

387
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:50,360
to remove martial officials from high rankings

388
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:53,000
and to adopt imperial sons to be his successor

389
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,800
by using rules and laws,

390
00:20:55,280 --> 00:20:56,880
so can His Majesty take away the firewood
from under the caldron

391
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:58,480
and put a huge hat

392
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,520
on Bao Zheng’s head,

393
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,520
stopping all the censors

394
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,920
from nagging and complaining

395
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:06,200
to earn a moment of peace.

396
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,720
Sirs, here’s the menu.

397
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:10,760
Please have a look.

398
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:15,460
= The Great Xiangguo Temple =

399
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:31,640
Prince Consort.

400
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:39,120
I’m princess’s eunuch.

401
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:41,240
I accompany Princess to offer incense.

402
00:21:42,080 --> 00:21:43,640
I didn’t wear uniform today

403
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:44,480
because I needed to buy something

404
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:46,440
in the market,

405
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,360
which made you misunderstand.

406
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:49,800
I’m deeply sorry.

407
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,160
I just got promoted to abbot.

408
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,640
It’s my first time to receive Princess.

409
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,320
I’m so sorry.

410
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,720
So sorry.

411
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,840
Don’t be nervous, master.

412
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,040
It’s not a big deal.

413
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:03,480
Amitabha.

414
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,160
Follow me, Princess.

415
00:22:17,280 --> 00:22:18,000
See,

416
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:20,120
you look good in the robe.

417
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,680
A perfect match for me.

418
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:23,920
Don’t wear uniform of eunuch

419
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:25,640
unless you need to go to the palace.

420
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:29,740
I asked Prince Consort to take a concubine, but he refused.

421
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:30,980
He doesn’t even

422
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,300
have dinner

423
00:22:32,300 --> 00:22:33,100
with Princess

424
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:34,260
nowadays.

425
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:37,100
He’ll either go out for days

426
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:38,300
with a bag of pigments,

427
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:40,260
or stay in his room all day long,

428
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:43,820
letting that woman

429
00:22:44,100 --> 00:22:45,500
have fun

430
00:22:45,980 --> 00:22:47,860
with the eunuch.

431
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,460
Look,

432
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:50,860
you’ve already said

433
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:52,660
he’s a eunuch.

434
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:54,580
Being mad at him

435
00:22:54,780 --> 00:22:56,260
is a humiliation to Prince Consort.

436
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:57,900
If His Majesty and Her Highness

437
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:59,180
hear about this,

438
00:22:59,180 --> 00:23:00,660
it will make us sound stingy.

439
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:03,340
Then, then I have to bear with it?

440
00:23:05,620 --> 00:23:07,220
The deathday of Lord Li is coming soon.

441
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:10,180
It’s time to use

442
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:12,340
the plan I told you last time.

443
00:23:14,460 --> 00:23:17,220
No matter how superior she is,

444
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,340
after experiencing that,

445
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:21,260
she’ll be Prince Consort’s woman.

446
00:23:21,980 --> 00:23:23,700
After she has children,

447
00:23:24,140 --> 00:23:24,980
I believe

448
00:23:25,420 --> 00:23:26,380
what she worries

449
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:28,780
will be if Prince Consort will take new concubines.

450
00:23:40,480 --> 00:23:41,280
Mr. Liang,

451
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,560
I have something to tell you.

452
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:55,080
Mr. Liang, please let Princess be
with Prince Consort.

453
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,520
What are you talking about?

454
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:03,000
We all want

455
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,600
Princess and Prince Consort to live a happy life.

456
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,280
But

457
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,480
but Princess

458
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:08,640
has someone in her heart.

459
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:12,160
If the one she loves always gives her hope,

460
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,720
she won’t even look at Prince Consort.

461
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:20,840
Mr. Cao…

462
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,840
I’m not talking about Mr. Cao.

463
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,120
Now Mr. Cao

464
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:26,920
is not in her heart anymore.

465
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:31,040
Mr. Liang,

466
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:35,000
you know Prince Consort is a good man,

467
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:38,840
and has great talent.

468
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:41,600
Even if

469
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:43,640
Princess sees his merits

470
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,880
and still can’t fall in love with him,

471
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,120
he can at least

472
00:24:48,120 --> 00:24:49,080
be a normal husband

473
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,520
giving Princess a normal life,

474
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,240
and,

475
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,400
and child,

476
00:24:58,600 --> 00:24:59,880
adorable children.

477
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:02,560
With them,

478
00:25:03,600 --> 00:25:06,920
all her loneliness

479
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:09,440
shall be gone.

480
00:25:42,770 --> 00:25:43,690
Huaiji,

481
00:25:45,890 --> 00:25:47,130
you are in my heart.

482
00:26:03,970 --> 00:26:04,810
Where’s Huaiji?

483
00:26:05,970 --> 00:26:06,970
Mr. Liang said

484
00:26:07,330 --> 00:26:08,970
he needs to check bills today.

485
00:26:09,050 --> 00:26:10,570
During the day he’s occupied by trivial things

486
00:26:10,570 --> 00:26:11,730
and the quietness of night

487
00:26:12,090 --> 00:26:13,130
can help him to focus on that.

488
00:26:37,570 --> 00:26:38,490
Let’s go back.

489
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:41,530
I’m tired.

490
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:54,550
Princess, Mr. Liang went out.

491
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:57,390
He said that you’ll go to the palace few days later

492
00:26:57,390 --> 00:26:58,990
to visit the two new born princesses,

493
00:26:59,430 --> 00:27:00,630
and he gave the purchasing list

494
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:01,830
to Bai last time

495
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:02,710
but the result was not satisfying,

496
00:27:03,190 --> 00:27:04,950
so today he went to purchase them himself

497
00:27:05,190 --> 00:27:06,830
to see if there’s anything new.

498
00:27:20,795 --> 00:27:27,557
♪ Memory is the breathe in deep sleep ♪

499
00:27:28,252 --> 00:27:35,128
♪ Surging in every gap ♪

500
00:27:35,587 --> 00:27:42,054
♪ Light dream is the bells under the roof ♪

501
00:27:42,522 --> 00:27:49,633
♪ Awakened by every blow ♪

502
00:27:50,429 --> 00:27:56,972
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

503
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:58,110
Princess.

504
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:00,670
You haven’t had dinner yet, right?

505
00:28:01,950 --> 00:28:02,670
Me,

506
00:28:02,670 --> 00:28:03,710
me neither.

507
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,310
I roasted some sweet potatoes.

508
00:28:05,510 --> 00:28:06,670
I want to eat them with you,

509
00:28:06,670 --> 00:28:07,430
one for each of us.

510
00:28:08,227 --> 00:28:12,160
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

511
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:18,475
♪ Regardless of the result ♪

512
00:28:23,941 --> 00:28:27,688
♪ Beautiful peach blossom in spring ♪

513
00:28:27,688 --> 00:28:30,960
♪ The red wall sighs for little wind and rain ♪

514
00:28:31,406 --> 00:28:34,505
♪ Innocent kids stand against the wall ♪

515
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:37,414
♪ Laughing at the butterfly for favoring its nectar ♪

516
00:28:37,430 --> 00:28:38,190
Here you are.

517
00:28:38,870 --> 00:28:39,710
Have it.

518
00:28:39,726 --> 00:28:42,475
♪ Beautiful peach blossom in spring ♪

519
00:28:42,475 --> 00:28:45,717
♪ Is perfect decoration for room, for house, and for couples ♪

520
00:28:46,210 --> 00:28:49,877
♪ We love deep, yet we don’t have the fate ♪

521
00:28:49,870 --> 00:28:52,336
♪ The fate picks the autumn to bestow a marriage ♪

522
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:54,750
Huaiji, I promise you

523
00:28:54,910 --> 00:28:57,390
I won’t come to see you during night.

524
00:28:57,870 --> 00:28:59,230
But you must promise me

525
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:02,710
not to be out of my sight.

526
00:29:03,710 --> 00:29:05,630
If you need to go outside,

527
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:07,550
you must tell me first.

528
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:15,830
And this, look.

529
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:16,710
Huaiji.

530
00:29:25,630 --> 00:29:26,430
Mr. Liang.

531
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:32,020
= Liang Quanyi =

532
00:29:32,230 --> 00:29:33,750
Why are those female Taoists

533
00:29:33,870 --> 00:29:35,150
who performed the rite for the tenth deathday of Lord Li

534
00:29:35,230 --> 00:29:36,590
still living in the mansion?

535
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,910
They moved in the backyard

536
00:29:40,230 --> 00:29:41,270
after they held the services for the departed soul.

537
00:29:42,670 --> 00:29:43,990
I don’t think those Taoists

538
00:29:44,430 --> 00:29:45,590
are decent people.

539
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:48,390
I wanted to send them out,

540
00:29:48,630 --> 00:29:49,470
worrying they might disgrace the mansion.

541
00:29:50,910 --> 00:29:53,350
But I think Mrs. Yang

542
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:57,950
wants to send them to serve the Prince Consort

543
00:29:58,430 --> 00:29:59,750
with the excuse of the rite.

544
00:30:02,950 --> 00:30:03,870
If you think

545
00:30:03,870 --> 00:30:04,670
there’s something inappropriate,

546
00:30:04,710 --> 00:30:05,950
I can talk to Mrs. Yang.

547
00:30:07,430 --> 00:30:08,110
Don’t.

548
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:12,390
Mrs. Yang invited them here.

549
00:30:12,870 --> 00:30:14,390
If you insist to send them out,

550
00:30:14,390 --> 00:30:15,670
it only hurts your relationship with her.

551
00:30:17,150 --> 00:30:19,310
Besides, Princess does not resist

552
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:20,790
Prince Consort being close with other girls.

553
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:23,230
Just be careful.

554
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:24,510
Protect Princess

555
00:30:24,510 --> 00:30:25,830
from them.

556
00:30:40,830 --> 00:30:41,510
Princess.

557
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:42,830
Huaiji.

558
00:30:43,230 --> 00:30:44,870
I got a tutti song.

559
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:49,590
Princess, Mrs. Yang just said

560
00:30:49,590 --> 00:30:51,390
it will be Prince Consort’s birthday in a few days

561
00:30:51,950 --> 00:30:52,910
and she wants to hold a birthday banquet.

562
00:30:54,830 --> 00:30:55,990
I don’t care.

563
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:03,230
Hauiji, find something

564
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:04,630
to give him

565
00:31:04,630 --> 00:31:05,550
as his birthday gift.

566
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:10,350
Mrs. Yang wants you to be present at the banquet.

567
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:13,670
After all, it’s only once in a year.

568
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:21,350
Well then.

569
00:31:22,070 --> 00:31:23,870
Li Wei hasn’t come to bother me
for quite some time.

570
00:31:24,950 --> 00:31:25,910
I can go.

571
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:29,190
Send him a huge gift.

572
00:31:29,830 --> 00:31:31,870
Hope we can stay separate

573
00:31:32,230 --> 00:31:33,670
like this in the future.

574
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,310
Then you go with me…

575
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,790
I have a lot of things to do.

576
00:31:37,910 --> 00:31:38,590
But

577
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:40,230
every time when I asked for your approval,

578
00:31:40,630 --> 00:31:42,310
you never allowed me to go outside.

579
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:44,590
How about this?

580
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,590
On the day of his banquet,

581
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:48,430
you go to celebrate his birthday,

582
00:31:49,230 --> 00:31:50,670
and I’ll go out to do my work.

583
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,710
I’ll manage to buy and do all the things

584
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:54,950
I need to do

585
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:55,910
within a day,

586
00:31:56,870 --> 00:31:57,950
and bring some roasted pork
from the Great Xiangguo Temple

587
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:59,750
to you.

588
00:32:05,950 --> 00:32:08,590
Then I’ll spend the day with him for his birthday,

589
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:10,510
but after then,

590
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:11,950
you’ll stay with me to play instruments

591
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:13,790
every day.

592
00:32:14,470 --> 00:32:16,910
I’ll play the harp and you’ll play the flute.

593
00:32:17,750 --> 00:32:18,910
Together we’ll

594
00:32:18,910 --> 00:32:19,670
make a perfect ensemble

595
00:32:20,190 --> 00:32:21,750
of this song,

596
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:23,870
that’s when you can go out of the mansion again.

597
00:32:40,470 --> 00:32:41,350
Princess.

598
00:32:42,580 --> 00:32:43,620
Please wait.

599
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:46,260
= Yuqing =
We stayed in your mansion

600
00:32:46,260 --> 00:32:47,220
for a few days

601
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:48,700
yet we haven’t greeted you.

602
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:50,580
We prepared several songs

603
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,500
for you on the birthday banquet.

604
00:32:59,860 --> 00:33:00,700
Please.

605
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:09,100
We made the wine ourselves.

606
00:33:09,340 --> 00:33:10,380
It’s called Peach Blossoms.

607
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:11,580
It tastes different from other wines.

608
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:13,300
Please try some.

609
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:29,300
Princess,

610
00:33:30,380 --> 00:33:32,500
that was my toast to you.

611
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:35,540
This is Fuyue’s toast to you.

612
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:38,460
If you like Fuyue’s singing,

613
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:39,540
please have this cup.

614
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:43,220
Tell her to sing another song.

615
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:45,580
If I like it,

616
00:33:46,060 --> 00:33:46,980
I’ll drink this cup.

617
00:33:47,460 --> 00:33:48,260
Okay.

618
00:33:50,380 --> 00:33:52,380
= Fuyue Zhuyun =

619
00:33:53,100 --> 00:33:57,500
♪ Riding a horse in a warm day ♪

620
00:33:57,700 --> 00:34:01,060
♪ Wandering on the paths ♪

621
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:04,340
♪ Green grass are waving on the field ♪

622
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:08,620
♪ And white catkins are fluttering in the wind ♪

623
00:34:10,180 --> 00:34:14,460
♪ An embroidered carriage moves the dust ♪

624
00:34:14,740 --> 00:34:18,989
♪ I can see a beautiful girl
sitting on the car with celestial beauty ♪

625
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:22,260
♪ I tried to get close ♪

626
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:29,060
♪ But I can’t talk with her ♪

627
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:31,080
You are all female Taoists,

628
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,840
I wonder

629
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,760
what Tao you are practicing?

630
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,440
Why

631
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:42,320
do you want to marry a man

632
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:44,360
and be a couple?

633
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:49,560
Practicing Tao doesn’t matter.

634
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:53,720
Our love hides deep in the garden.

635
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:58,520
Well then,

636
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:02,280
I’ll give you your love.

637
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:06,000
Thank you, Princess.

638
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:13,600
I’m tired. I’ll go to rest now.

639
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:16,360
You are young, and it’s a rare chance.

640
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,280
Just have more fun,

641
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,960
and enjoy more songs from them.

642
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:30,960
Are you doing okay?

643
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:34,400
Have another cup, Princess.

644
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:43,660
♪ My eyebrow was ruined in his arm yet
I haven’t repainted it ♪

645
00:35:45,250 --> 00:35:52,330
♪ My make-up was messed up in drunkenness ♪

646
00:35:52,340 --> 00:35:54,400
♪ I hold tight to my lover and cling on him ♪

647
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:56,020
The girl in the song

648
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:57,370
gets drunk

649
00:35:57,750 --> 00:35:58,900
and ruins her make-up,

650
00:35:59,250 --> 00:36:00,760
which has nothing to do with her lover,

651
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:03,510
why does she cling on him?

652
00:36:03,820 --> 00:36:06,330
The make-up is on her face,

653
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:07,740
and she can’t kiss it herself,

654
00:36:08,370 --> 00:36:09,460
so it must be someone else

655
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:10,940
who’s drunk.

656
00:36:14,070 --> 00:36:14,980
Prince Consort,

657
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:17,090
your wife is tired.

658
00:36:17,170 --> 00:36:18,560
Don’t you come and hold her?

659
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:20,920
Are you doing okay?

660
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:32,420
= Princess’s Mansion =

661
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:55,840
Where’s Princess?

662
00:36:59,660 --> 00:37:03,460
♪ We cried when we meet again ♪

663
00:37:03,740 --> 00:37:07,580
♪ We had sex after drinking ♪

664
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:11,860
♪ We sleep together on a beautiful bed ♪

665
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,309
♪ The romantic smell ♪

666
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:25,980
Mr. Liang,

667
00:37:26,580 --> 00:37:27,580
I’ll just tell you the truth

668
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:29,140
today.

669
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:32,700
Tonight, Prince Consort and Princess

670
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,620
consummated their marriage
out of their own willing.

671
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,060
It has nothing to do with you,

672
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:37,660
and you can do nothing about it.

673
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:40,140
Go back and have a rest.

674
00:37:40,380 --> 00:37:41,660
Come back tomorrow to congratulate them.

675
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:43,260
I’ll tell Prince Consort

676
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:45,580
to prepare a huge award for you.

677
00:37:47,580 --> 00:37:48,660
Stop him!

678
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:54,140
You can’t force Princess

679
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:55,860
to do what she doesn’t want to do.

680
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:58,260
You all saw what happened

681
00:37:58,340 --> 00:38:00,020
here just now.

682
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:02,860
Princess drank wine with Prince Consort

683
00:38:03,180 --> 00:38:04,700
and went to his bedroom

684
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:06,100
to rest hand in hand.

685
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:07,340
Who said she doesn’t want to do this?

686
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:08,660
You know

687
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:09,980
if she wants or not.

688
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,180
Have you considered

689
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:12,180
the consequence?

690
00:38:14,140 --> 00:38:15,140
You mean

691
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,660
you’ll report me

692
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,700
to His Majesty and Her Highness?

693
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:22,180
A mother-in-law brings Princess
and Prince Consort together.

694
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,060
How can that be wrong?

695
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:24,300
Don’t forget

696
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,540
His Majesty wants to have grandsons soon.

697
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:29,700
If you want to go to the palace

698
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:30,980
and make something up about me and Prince Consort,

699
00:38:31,620 --> 00:38:33,340
be careful that you might miscalculate.

700
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:34,660
His Majesty might

701
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:36,660
punish you for sowing discord

702
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:38,180
between Princess and Prince Consort.

703
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:39,620
She’ll die!

704
00:38:41,540 --> 00:38:42,460
Stop him!

705
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:44,780
What are you going! Where are you going!

706
00:38:46,429 --> 00:38:47,642
Stop him!

707
00:38:47,740 --> 00:38:48,700
Stop him!

708
00:38:49,380 --> 00:38:50,340
Stop him now!

709
00:38:50,362 --> 00:38:51,877
Don’t let him get away!

710
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:52,884
Stop him.

711
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:54,620
Get up and stop him!

712
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:16,460
Princess, let’s go home.

713
00:40:25,580 --> 00:40:26,300
Huirou.

714
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:28,660
Huirou.

715
00:40:46,810 --> 00:40:53,770
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

716
00:40:54,330 --> 00:41:01,250
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

717
00:41:01,730 --> 00:41:08,090
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

718
00:41:08,530 --> 00:41:15,290
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

719
00:41:16,530 --> 00:41:23,330
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

720
00:41:23,930 --> 00:41:30,650
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

721
00:41:31,210 --> 00:41:38,250
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

722
00:41:38,250 --> 00:41:45,090
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

723
00:41:49,970 --> 00:41:53,490
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

724
00:41:53,690 --> 00:41:57,290
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

725
00:41:57,290 --> 00:42:00,490
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

726
00:42:00,490 --> 00:42:04,890
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

727
00:42:04,890 --> 00:42:08,610
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

728
00:42:08,610 --> 00:42:12,170
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

729
00:42:12,170 --> 00:42:15,890
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

730
00:42:15,890 --> 00:42:21,650
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

731
00:42:23,410 --> 00:42:26,570
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

732
00:42:27,090 --> 00:42:30,450
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

733
00:42:30,690 --> 00:42:33,970
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

734
00:42:33,970 --> 00:42:38,330
♪ He plays with the butterfly gathering honey ♪

735
00:42:38,330 --> 00:42:41,490
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

736
00:42:41,970 --> 00:42:45,650
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

737
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:49,330
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

